And then I noticed
a couple more.

21:26.077 --> 21:27.868
[moans]

21:27.912 --> 21:29.537
<i>¶ ¶</i>

21:29.580 --> 21:31.420
- Right now, he's trying
to soften up that spot

21:31.457 --> 21:32.957
where he sees that crack,

21:33.001 --> 21:34.709
'cause if it's hard steel,

21:34.752 --> 21:37.753
it is more likely
to fracture during a chop.

21:37.797 --> 21:39.797
<i>- Where the cracks are
shouldn't be</i>

21:39.841 --> 21:41.382
<i>too much of a problem.</i>

21:41.426 --> 21:43.467
I'm just gonna keep
my fingers crossed.

21:43.511 --> 21:45.761
- You have 30 minutes remaining!

21:45.805 --> 21:49.724
<i>[rock music]</i>

21:49.767 --> 21:50.891
- Tobin's having some issues

21:50.935 --> 21:52.268
trying to drill
through that tang.

21:52.312 --> 21:53.602
- Sometimes the smaller
doesn't work;

21:53.646 --> 21:55.229
you got to go bigger.

21:55.273 --> 21:56.814
- Go big or go home, apparently.

21:56.858 --> 21:58.691
<i>¶ ¶</i>

21:58.735 --> 22:00.901
[metal grinding]

22:00.945 --> 22:02.153
- Ooh!

22:02.196 --> 22:03.279
- I'm on the drill press,

22:03.323 --> 22:05.156
<i>trying to get the bit through,</i>

22:05.199 --> 22:07.700
and you hear that screech.

22:07.744 --> 22:11.746
[metal grinding]

22:11.789 --> 22:14.248
It just tells you
you hit a hard spot.

22:14.292 --> 22:17.293
[metal grinding]

22:19.547 --> 22:20.547
- [bleep].

22:23.885 --> 22:24.885
[metal grinding]

22:31.893 --> 22:33.809
[metal grinding]
<i>- I'm on the drill press,</i>

22:33.853 --> 22:36.645
and you hear that screech.

22:36.689 --> 22:39.648
[metal grinding]

22:39.692 --> 22:43.194
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

22:43.237 --> 22:45.696
I knew I'd hit a hard spot.

22:45.740 --> 22:46.947
We go to plan B!

22:46.991 --> 22:48.407
- Five minutes, gentlemen.

22:48.451 --> 22:52.328
You have five minutes remaining.

22:52.372 --> 22:56.624
<i>- Plan B was
just to do a handle wrap.</i>

22:56.667 --> 22:59.627
The blade basically said,
"Hey, I need paracord.

22:59.670 --> 23:01.087
Forget the wood crap."

23:01.130 --> 23:02.755
<i>[rock music]</i>

23:02.799 --> 23:06.050
<i>It just fit the overall
postapocalyptic,</i>

23:06.094 --> 23:09.345
strange, crazy kind of feel
I was going for

23:09.389 --> 23:11.472
<i>with that dramatic
blade shape anyway.</i>

23:11.516 --> 23:14.809
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

23:14.852 --> 23:18.479
- Ten, nine, eight,

23:18.523 --> 23:22.191
seven, six, five,

23:22.235 --> 23:27.488
four, three, two, one.

